N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 11 ยง 96.11 - Accounts already established

State Regulations

Every company which is already maintaining a surplus management account shall submit to the superintendent, within 30 days after the promulgation of this Part, for approval in accordance with this Part, a plan with respect to the existing surplus management account. Notes
